---
title: Southeast Asian Tofu Bowl with Ginger Veggies & Garlic Rice
description: We love rice bowls because they’re so easy to customise with your favourite flavours. This veggie version uses Peking marinated tofu, Asian greens, carrot and cucumber, with a sweet chilli sauce to tie the whole thing together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southeast-asian-tofu-bowl-b166692d.jpg
